      <h1>Digital Marketing & Its Types</h1>
      <p>
        A simple guide to what digital marketing is, why it matters, and the key channels:
        SEO, SEM/PPC, Social Media, Content, Email, Affiliate, Influencer, Mobile, and Analytics & CRO.
